  "texts": [
    "Infiltrated leaves were collected 5 days after infiltration and homogenized with virus inoculation buffer (10 mM monopotassium phosphate containing 1% Celite (Thermo Fisher Scientific, 68855-54-9)).",
    "The homogenate containing viral particles was rub inoculated onto five to ten seedlings of TA1675 at the three leaf stage.",
    "After two weeks of recovery and viral symptoms appearing, the seedlings were inoculated with Pt isolate B9414.",
    "Prior to inoculating TA1675, Pt isolate B9414 was propagated on seedlings of the susceptible wheat cultivar Thatcher.",
    "Freshly collected urediniospores were suspended in Isopar L and sprayed onto plants using a high-pressure air sprayer."
  ],
